<description>

After login, the Product Inventory page lists all products with name, description, price, and an "Add to cart" button. A sort dropdown allows sorting by name (A–Z, Z–A) and price (low–high, high–low). Clicking a product name or image opens the Product Detail page. Clicking "Add to cart" adds the item and changes the button to "Remove"; the cart badge count updates accordingly. Clicking "Remove" reverses the action.


</description>

<workflows>
WF-001 | Open All Items from header menu | actor: Authenticated user | branch: none | terminal: All Items | on_success: navigates to All Items page
WF-002 | Open About from header menu | actor: Authenticated user | branch: none | terminal: About | on_success: navigates to About page
WF-003 | Logout via header menu | actor: Authenticated user | branch: none | terminal: Logout | on_success: logs out and navigates to sign-in page
WF-004 | Reset app state via header menu | actor: Authenticated user | branch: none | terminal: Reset App State | on_success: resets application state to default
WF-005 | Open Cart (proceed to Checkout) | actor: Authenticated user | branch: none | terminal: Cart | on_success: navigates to Checkout sequence (Information → Overview → Confirmation)
WF-006 | Change sort order | actor: Authenticated user | branch: none | terminal: Sort_By | on_success: products reordered according to selected sort option
WF-007 | Open Product Detail by clicking product name | actor: Authenticated user | branch: none | terminal: Product_Name | on_success: opens Product Detail page
WF-008 | Open Product Detail by clicking product image | actor: Authenticated user | branch: none | terminal: Product_Image | on_success: opens Product Detail page
WF-009 | Add item to cart (item not currently in cart) | actor: Authenticated user | branch: Item_In_Cart == false | terminal: Add to cart | on_success: adds item to cart, increments cart badge count, button state changes to Remove
WF-010 | Remove item from cart (item currently in cart) | actor: Authenticated user | branch: Item_In_Cart == true | terminal: Remove | on_success: removes item from cart, decrements cart badge count, button state changes to Add to cart
</workflows>

